INSERT INTO `wp_comments` VALUES (1,1,'Monsieur WordPress','','https://wordpress.org/','','2015-12-03 17:50:07','2015-12-03 16:50:07','Bonjour, ceci est un commentaire.\nPour supprimer un commentaire, connectez-vous et affichez les commentaires de cet article. Vous pourrez alors les modifier ou les supprimer.',0,'1','','',0,0),(2,13,'Ashley Cooper','info@demolink.org','','192.168.1.1','2015-10-06 14:22:17','2015-10-06 14:22:17','Now I know what colors to choose for me office, thank you!',0,'1','','',0,0),(3,13,'Gomez Bell','info@demolink.org','','192.168.1.1','2015-10-06 14:22:48','2015-10-06 14:22:48','The repairing does not seem that challenging any more. Great tips!',0,'1','','',0,0),(4,13,'Morgan Cook','info@demolink.org','','192.168.1.1','2015-10-06 14:23:20','2015-10-06 14:23:20','Colors that stimulate the employees, relax the customers and make them feel welcome… Cool! That’s a dream!',0,'1','','',0,0),(5,14,'Libi Ramirez','info@demolink.org','','192.168.1.1','2015-10-06 14:13:49','2015-10-06 14:13:49','Communication is the process of exchanging information in the form of messages, symbols, thoughts, signs, and opinions. It’s utterly important for such social beings like people.',0,'1','','',0,0),(6,14,'Kirsten Evans','info@demolink.org','','192.168.1.1','2015-10-06 14:14:11','2015-10-06 14:14:11','Indeed, it would be extremely hard to imagine a world without some form of interpersonal interaction.',0,'1','','',0,0),(7,14,'Brook Murphy','info@demolink.org','','192.168.1.1','2015-10-06 14:14:33','2015-10-06 14:14:33','Some of the basic ways by which we communicate with one another is through speech, sign language, body language, touch, and eye contact. So, waiting for the sequel of your post.',0,'1','','',0,0),(8,15,'Rob Gonzalez','info@demolink.org','','192.168.1.1','2015-10-06 14:08:00','2015-10-06 14:08:00','Thanks for your pieces of advice. Will try to stick to them.',0,'1','','',0,0),(9,15,'Paul Young','info@demolink.org','','192.168.1.1','2015-10-06 14:08:20','2015-10-06 14:08:20','Gosh! I have been slowly damaging my heart all these years! It’s time to stop ruining myself.',0,'1','','',0,0),(10,15,'Sandy Hill','info@demolink.org','','192.168.1.1','2015-10-06 14:09:22','2015-10-06 14:09:22','Human life is the most precious thing in this world. It’s really time to stop committing lazy suicides.',0,'1','','',0,0),(11,16,'Joe Lee','info@demolink.org','','192.168.1.1','2015-10-06 13:58:32','2015-10-06 13:58:32','Very inspiring! So much wisdom in simple words…',0,'1','','',0,0),(12,16,'Kate Taylor','info@demolink.org','','192.168.1.1','2015-10-06 13:58:52','2015-10-06 13:58:52','Love this poet! Absolutely brilliant quotes!',0,'1','','',0,0),(13,16,'Kim Martin','info@demolink.org','','192.168.1.1','2015-10-06 13:59:12','2015-10-06 13:59:12','He is phenomenal! Rumi is considered to be the most popular poet in America.',0,'1','','',0,0),(14,17,'Zack Hernandez','info@demolink.org','','192.168.1.1','2015-10-06 13:47:54','2015-10-06 13:47:54','The success of your business would solely depend on you. The only thing you can rely on is your power to achieve your goal\" – very true to life statement.',0,'1','','',0,0),(15,17,'Greg Wilson','info@demolink.org','','192.168.1.1','2015-10-06 13:48:27','2015-10-06 13:48:27','Unbelievable… Three simple guidelines to follow that can change your life. Worth trying out, sure they will work as everything genius is simple.',0,'1','','',0,0),(16,17,'James Anderson','info@demolink.org','','192.168.1.1','2015-10-06 13:54:19','2015-10-06 13:54:19','I am thinking of starting my own business and will ponder on the author’s notes. Concise and understandable, good job.',0,'1','','',0,0),(17,18,'Taylor Miller','info@demolink.org','','192.168.1.1','2015-10-06 13:40:44','2015-10-06 13:40:44','Follow your dream and it will turn to reality. A very inspiring article. Thanks for sharing!',0,'1','','',0,0),(18,18,'Max Harris','info@demolink.org','','192.168.1.1','2015-10-06 13:41:38','2015-10-06 13:41:38','