oks much more appealing and beautiful too.',0,'1','','',0,0),(28,21,'Vivien Foster','info@demolink.org','','192.168.51.93','2015-10-08 13:26:40','2015-10-08 13:26:40','I like to spread my laughter around as it\'s contagious.',0,'1','','',0,0),(29,22,'Nancy Long','info@demolink.org','','192.168.51.93','2015-10-08 13:11:51','2015-10-08 13:11:51','Thanks for sharing! Will try to avoid the listed mistakes.',0,'1','','',0,0),(30,22,'Eva Reed','info@demolink.org','','192.168.51.93','2015-10-08 13:12:17','2015-10-08 13:12:17','I wish I’ve read this article earlier… Useful tips for all young managers.',0,'1','','',0,0),(31,22,'Betty Butler','info@demolink.org','','192.168.51.93','2015-10-08 13:12:33','2015-10-08 13:12:33','Just got my new position. The discussed matter is really urgent for me.',0,'1','','',0,0);
